                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="changes__item-galleria">
                        <a href="/assets/image/changes/changes_1.png" class="modal-image">
                            <img class="changes__item-image" src="/assets/image/changes/changes_1.png" alt="#">
                        </a>
                        <a href="/assets/image/changes/changes_1.png" class="modal-image">
                            <img class="changes__item-image" src="/assets/image/changes/changes_1.png" alt="#">
                        </a>
                        <a href="/assets/image/changes/changes_1.png" class="modal-image">
                            <img class="changes__item-image" src="/assets/image/changes/changes_1.png" alt="#">
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="changes__item-content">
                        <h3 class="changes__item-title">Поликлиника МВД №1</h3>
                        <span class="changes__item-caption">Адрес объекта Москва, Петровка, 25а ст1</span>
                        <span class="changes__item-caption">Сроки выполнения 60 дней</span>
                        <span class="changes__item-caption">Количество альпинистов 6 человек</span>
                        <span class="changes__item-caption">Вид работ Капитальный ремонт фасада здания</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
